Package com.linkedin.venice.pubsub.adapter

Class PubSubSharedProducerFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.linkedin.venice.pubsub.adapter.PubSubSharedProducerFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PubSubProducerAdapterFactory<PubSubSharedProducerAdapter>, java.io.Closeable, java.lang.AutoCloseable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SharedKafkaProducerAdapterFactory
    public abstract class PubSubSharedProducerFactory
extends java.lang.Object
implements PubSubProducerAdapterFactory<PubSubSharedProducerAdapter>
    This abstract class provides common functionality required to create and track shared producers. This service maintains a pool of shared producers. Ingestion task can acquire or release a producer on demand basis. It does lazy initialization of producers. Also, producers are assigned based on the least loaded manner.
